      "body" : "actually BOTH are correct, it depends on how it is used: it can be <code>java -Dspring.profiles.active=staging -Dspring.config.location=C:\\Config your-spring-boot-app.jar</code> OR <code>java your-spring-boot.jar --spring.profiles.active=staging --spring.config.location=C:\\Config</code>"
