    "answer_id" : 37872196,
    "question_id" : 31038250,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>you can use the following command line:</p>\n\n<pre><code>java -jar -Dspring.profiles.active=[yourProfileName] target/[yourJar].jar\n</code></pre>\n"
