    "question_id" : 31038250,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>A way that i do this on intellij is setting an environment variable on the command like so:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/EiL0d.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/EiL0d.png\" alt=\"test setup on intellij\" /></a></p>\n<p>In this case i am setting the profile to test</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 4489017,
      "reputation" : 391,
      "user_id" : 3650655,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/6b43e8ceee2665d21f8992fa5532981c?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "user3650655",
